full_text:
Nicely said Jay!

In the end, does your device work?  That is the only thing that&#39;s important.  Anyone can clip a wire and get spirit communication, but few actually take it upon themselves to try to design something that can improve the communications with spirits.

Maybe if people didn&#39;t get so offended and worked together this research could truly advance instead of remaining stagnant.

For the work I do, I need to have the most reliable spirit communication device.  I find radios to be a very poor tool, but a tool non the less.  No matter how well the sweep circuit works, it is still a radio.  That is why I got out of the box and started testing to determine the extents of what the spirits can affect so I can build something more reliable.

lets move forward.

-Chris


